          "answer": "We offer a variety of <a href=\"https://www.clickeen.com/\" class=\"diet-dropdown-edit-link\"></a><a href=\"https://www.clickeen.com/\" class=\"diet-dropdown-edit-link\"></a><a href=\"https://www.clickeen.com/\" class=\"diet-dropdown-edit-link\">modern art exhibits</a> including <a href=\"https://www.clickeen.com/\" class=\"diet-dropdown-edit-link\"></a><a href=\"https://www.clickeen.com/\" class=\"diet-dropdown-edit-link\"></a><a href=\"https://www.clickeen.com/\" class=\"diet-dropdown-edit-link\">contemporary artists</a> , sculptures, and <a href=\"https://www.clickeen.com/\" class=\"diet-dropdown-edit-link\"></a><a href=\"https://www.clickeen.com/\" class=\"diet-dropdown-edit-link\"></a><a href=\"https://www.clickeen.com/\" class=\"diet-dropdown-edit-link\">installations</a> .",
          "defaultOpen": false,
          "id": "q1",
          "question": "What types of art exhibits are available?"
        },
        {
          "answer": "The museum is open daily from 10 AM to 6 PM.",
          "defaultOpen": false,
          "id": "q3",
          "question": "What are the visiting hours?"
        },
        {
          "answer": "No, all ages are welcome.",
          "defaultOpen": false,
